 on the premium between LDO perpetual price and spot index. The protocol's cross-margin system allows efficient capital utilization across multiple positions. Funding payments are automatically debited or credited to trader accounts based on long/short position direction and the current rate. Vertex's off-chain sequencer enables rapid rate updates while maintaining on-chain settlement integrity."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
